upcoming.title: Robot Kinematics
upcoming.desc: Here you will learn basic robot kinematics. join in at the time given to learn more and build robots with us. starts from complete basic and we continue from there and grow together. To register, click on the button and fill the google form provided with your college email id and have a nice time.
